The paper proposes a new framework for hierarchical reinforcement learning (HRL) with multiple levels, which is a popular topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence. The paper focuses on improving the diversity of subpolicies, which is a key aspect of HRL. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.MA (Multiagent Systems).
